Class JoxyRootPaneUI

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.plaf.ComponentUI
      • javax.swing.plaf.RootPaneUI
        • javax.swing.plaf.basic.BasicRootPaneUI
          • joxy.JoxyRootPaneUI
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PropertyChangeListener, EventListener

    public class JoxyRootPaneUI
extends BasicRootPaneUI
    Joxy's UI delegate for the JRootPaneUI.

    This class is responsible for drawing the radial background of windows. Several ways of caching are used, since this is done very often. See backgroundCache, radialGradient600px and currentCache.

    Author:
    Thom Castermans, Willem Sonke
